     app._EWC.HDRSв†ђвЉѓWSS.Conx[(ВЇ8в†‘ВЁWSS.Conx[;1])вЌівЉ‚,'ZI8' вЋ•FMT con;2]
     :If 0в‰ app.вЋ•NC 'workNamespace' вЌќ /// change this name in DWI
        appв†ђapp.workNamespace
     :EndIf
     :If (3=app.вЋ•NC fn)в€§MODEв‰ 0
